  c   12.60120 '12.60120  'latpars  c @ 12.60120 '12.60120
  al  90.00000  
  be  107.25700 '107.25700   'latpars  be @ 107.25700 '107.25700
  ga  90.00000  
 
'atom basis in the unit cell 
  site O1 x 0.2474 y 1.0061 z 0.24799 occ O 1.0 beq 0.0521
  site O2 x 0.5363 y 0.9973 z 0.32620 occ O 1.0 beq 0.0417
  site O3 x 0.8278 y 0.9998 z 0.39530 occ O 1.0 beq 0.0574
  site C1 x 0.3523 y 0.6920 z 0.38640 occ C 1.0 beq 0.0300
  site C2 x 0.1887 y 0.5886 z 0.37750 occ C 1.0 beq 0.0371
  site C3 x 0.8260 y 0.6094 z 0.55250 occ C 1.0 beq 0.0372
  site C4 x 0.6773 y 0.6997 z 0.47420 occ C 1.0 beq 0.0309
  site C5 x 0.5071 y 0.5996 z 0.46440 occ C 1.0 beq 0.0264
  site C6 x 0.3673 y 0.9051 z 0.31440 occ C 1.0 beq 0.0359
  site C7 x 0.6938 y 0.9043 z 0.39880 occ C 1.0 beq 0.0377
  site H2 x 0.0840 y 0.6440 z 0.3270 occ H 1.0 beq 0.0420
  site H3 x 0.9420 y 0.6770 z 0.5590 occ H 1.0 beq 0.0520

  prm avrg_size_ntcda -61.5220863`_1.10138106
